articles.author: Nicholas Jasinski
articles.title: The Stock Market Had a Great Start to 2023. Earnings Season Could Be a Problem. - Barron's
articles.description: The S&P 500 had its best week since November. Reports from JPMorgan Chase and Bank of America will be among those that could confirm the rally—or send shares sliding.
articles.content:
Investors got their Goldilocks jobs report on Friday morning, with a growing-but-slowing labor market, a tick-up in participation, and a deceleration in the pace of wage gains.
